
Please use for the different collections the different downloader scripts.

Each downloader takes in account the montly and archive CH items only. 
It is not meant to be used for download of actual daily datasets. Daily datasets can be downloaded from the respective daily items. 
Not all parameters are available for all year. For surface based grid e.g. only the reconstructed parameters go back 'til 1864. The normal ones are only available since 1961/1971. 


